# Writing Style

## No Em Dashes

Do not use em dashes (—) in:
- Website copy (UI text, labels, descriptions, helper text)
- AI prompts sent to Anthropic or other LLMs
- User-facing content

Use alternatives instead:
- Commas for pauses
- Colons for introductions
- Periods for separate sentences
- Hyphens (-) for compound words

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
"Early to mid-stage companies — developing novel therapeutics"

// ✅ GOOD
"Early to mid-stage companies developing novel therapeutics"
```
